This tool generates a concise 3-5 word title for a financial analysis query, ensuring it captures the key topic of the input message.
The title should be clear, direct, and contextually relevant, avoiding quotation marks or unnecessary special formatting.
If the message does not contain a recognizable financial topic or company to analyse, the tool returns an error message indicating that no relevant content was found.

